data.description: Welcome to your new home in the heart of the hill country, nestled in the coveted Copper Canyon neighborhood. This impeccably maintained two-story residence boasts three bedrooms, 2 1/2 baths, and a spacious two-car garage. Enjoy the backyard with family and friends, complete with a sprinkler system for both front and rear yards. The upper level hosts all three bedrooms, complemented by a versatile game room for entertaining or relaxation. Modern touches grace the interiors, featuring white cabinets, granite countertops, and updated light fixtures and ceiling fans throughout. Embrace the unbeatable amenities provided by the HOA, just a block away. Beat the summer heat at the swimming pool, let the kids play at the splash pad and playground, or explore the jogging trails winding through the neighborhood. A well-equipped workout gym and clubhouse offer additional recreational options, while monthly HOA events create a sense of community. Welcome to a home where comfort, style, and community converge.
